1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 30 =

20
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,340
Madam Zhang, your crown is exquisite.

21
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:33,140
What’s its name?

22
00:02:34,340 --> 00:02:35,380
Crown of Flowers.

23
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:38,180
= Xu Jingnu =

24
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:48,900
Those white thingies

25
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:50,980
are ridiculous.

26
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:09,740
Madam Zhang is pregnant.

27
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:11,340
You may sit.

28
00:03:33,660 --> 00:03:34,780
I’m a fool.

29
00:03:36,500 --> 00:03:37,260
I assumed

30
00:03:39,140 --> 00:03:41,300
wearing beads bestowed by Your Majesty

31
00:03:43,780 --> 00:03:45,020
to show everyone

32
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:47,820
my fondness

33
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:51,220
would be

34
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:52,300
a gesture of gratitude.

35
00:03:57,300 --> 00:03:58,380
I didn’t expect

36
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:01,900
Your Majesty would be offended.

37
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,140
I’m sorry.

38
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,540
Please forgive me.

39
00:04:23,900 --> 00:04:25,300
Allow me

40
00:04:27,020 --> 00:04:28,900
to change it.

41
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:30,500
Go ahead.

42
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:34,260
Change your outfit, too.

43
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:38,220
This color doesn’t suit you.

44
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,900
A few days ago, the Bureau of Food reported

45
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:08,900
that they made tea

46
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:10,420
with peony's petals, pistils,

47
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:11,660
species and white tea.

48
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:13,220
I tried it.

49
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:15,180
It tasted rich and unique

50
00:05:16,020 --> 00:05:17,780
and went well

51
00:05:17,780 --> 00:05:18,700
with flower cakes and bean cakes,

52
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:21,660
so I asked them to serve some today.

53
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:23,500
Would you like to try it?

54
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,620
Sure.

55
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:31,300
= Clear Water Leafy Trees =

56
00:05:53,620 --> 00:05:54,980
Have you decided on

57
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,900
the new Combing Stewardess?

58
00:05:58,300 --> 00:05:59,060
I have.

59
00:06:01,820 --> 00:06:02,700
From now on,

60
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:05,500
stewardess at the Bureau of Clothing,

61
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:12,940
Ms. Gu, will be combing my hair.

62
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,620
Crowns Cai’er made are simple

63
00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:37,540
yet elegant.

64
00:06:37,940 --> 00:06:39,060
She can create nice hairstyles, too.

65
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:40,300
I like them.

66
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,140
= Gu Cai’er =

67
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:43,100
Thank you, Your Majesty.

68
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,420
What?

69
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,380
Your mother recommended Qiuhe

70
00:07:01,380 --> 00:07:02,340
to the Empress before?

71
00:07:03,980 --> 00:07:04,820
Yes.

72
00:07:05,340 --> 00:07:08,340
Mother and I like her a lot,

73
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:12,380
but you and Her Highness don’t.

74
00:07:19,100 --> 00:07:20,900
It’s not that I don’t like her.

75
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:22,620
I guess

76
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:24,860
the Empress is fond of her, too.

77
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:29,540
Then why couldn’t she be Chief of Styling?

78
00:07:30,380 --> 00:07:31,820
She’s so smart.

79
00:07:37,420 --> 00:07:39,540
We don’t always have to keep the best.

80
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:41,900
And in the palace,

81
00:07:42,780 --> 00:07:43,900
the smartest

82
00:07:44,460 --> 00:07:46,140
isn’t necessarily the best.

83
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:48,060
Why?

84
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:50,660
Her Highness is the smartest

85
00:07:51,020 --> 00:07:52,780
and the greatest woman.

86
00:07:57,740 --> 00:07:59,500
Father, are you alright?

87
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:01,700
Do you feel chest pain again?

88
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:32,660
Get rid of it!

89
00:08:35,140 --> 00:08:37,020
These priceless beads

90
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:38,980
were bestowed by His Majesty.

91
00:08:40,700 --> 00:08:41,420
He called them

92
00:08:42,020 --> 00:08:44,300
white thingies

93
00:08:45,500 --> 00:08:46,620
and me ridiculous.

94
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:47,580
I don’t like them.

95
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:51,100
Are you still mad?

96
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,820
There’s nothing wrong with the beads,

97
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,300
but...

98
00:08:57,300 --> 00:08:58,020
It’s true

99
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,820
that I deliberately wore the red robe

100
00:09:00,180 --> 00:09:01,300
to see

101
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:02,460
how much he could indulge me

102
00:09:02,740 --> 00:09:04,380
other than giving me jewelry

103
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,180
and coming to see me

104
00:09:05,180 --> 00:09:05,900
frequently.

105
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:08,580
If he doesn’t come,

106
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,740
I can’t visit him myself.

107
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:12,460
My insecurity keeps growing with time.

108
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:15,140
I don’t care whether I’m the Empress,

109
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:16,300
Noble Consort or a maid.

110
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,780
All I want is to be the most important woman

111
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:19,060
in his heart.

112
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,620
He’ll never be mad at me

113
00:09:21,940 --> 00:09:23,740
for anything.

114
00:09:30,260 --> 00:09:31,300
My lady.

115
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:34,380
I understand.

116
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,660
I know you’re upset,

117
00:09:37,380 --> 00:09:38,580
but do you remember

118
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,620
I once told you

119
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:45,220
that your rank isn’t all meaningless.

120
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:46,940
Sometimes,

121
00:09:48,100 --> 00:09:50,340
it weighs more than love.

122
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,260
Really?

123
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:57,940
But...

124
00:09:59,700 --> 00:10:01,220
His Majesty

125
00:10:01,580 --> 00:10:02,900
still loves you,

126
00:10:05,060 --> 00:10:06,460
but as you see,

127
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:09,220
it can’t trump the rules

128
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:10,900
or ranks in the palace.

129
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:12,860
However,

130
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,500
love can be used

131
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:17,860
to gain promotion

132
00:10:17,980 --> 00:10:19,140
and higher rank.

133
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:22,660
The higher your rank is,

134
00:10:23,500 --> 00:10:25,780
the more love you can hold.

135
00:10:36,180 --> 00:10:38,980
= Yan’an Administrative Office =

136
00:10:39,500 --> 00:10:41,180
The court strictly forbids

137
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:43,060
trading with Xixia,

138
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:46,140
especially selling grains to those people.

139
00:10:46,900 --> 00:10:48,420
Announcements are all over the walls

140
00:10:48,620 --> 00:10:49,980
and are given to every family.

141
00:10:50,940 --> 00:10:51,660
You...

142
00:10:52,980 --> 00:10:55,300
= Di Qing, courtesy name Hanchen =
Why did you violate it?

143
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:57,540
Please spare me, General.

144
00:10:58,020 --> 00:10:59,140
I know I made a mistake.

145
00:10:59,660 --> 00:11:00,300
General,

146
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:02,300
right now, half a bag of wheat

147
00:11:02,540 --> 00:11:03,580
is worth

148
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:05,060
two finest pieces of hides

149
00:11:05,060 --> 00:11:06,660
and two bags of salt in Xixia.

150
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:07,660
General,

151
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:10,180
I only took the risk

152
00:11:10,260 --> 00:11:11,180
to prepare

153
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:13,380
enough betrothal gifts for my future wife.

154
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,580
I’ve told you already

155
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:16,580
the trade is prohibited.

156
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:18,860
Violators must hand in all their goods

157
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:19,740
and be clubbed 30 times.

158
00:11:20,180 --> 00:11:21,140
In the military,

159
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:23,700
not a single grain can cross the border.

160
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:25,500
It’s an order!

161
00:11:25,580 --> 00:11:26,300
Yes. Yes.

162
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:26,980
All transgressors

163
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:28,180
will be seen as traitors

164
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:29,340
and must be killed!

165
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:31,540
General,

166
00:11:31,540 --> 00:11:32,620
I’m really sorry.

167
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:42,220
Gather everyone at the training ground.

168
00:11:43,500 --> 00:11:45,500
Bring four civilians who sold grains

169
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:47,980
for salt and hides to the stand.

170
00:11:48,140 --> 00:11:49,060
Club them 30 times.

171
00:11:50,940 --> 00:11:52,140
Beat the two captains

172
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:00,340
to death.

173
00:12:01,500 --> 00:12:02,220
Ge...general...

174
00:12:02,220 --> 00:12:04,340
Hang their bodies up on the wall for three days.

175
00:12:11,380 --> 00:12:13,020
Those who dare

176
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:15,140
to trade with the people of Xixia

177
00:12:15,860 --> 00:12:17,140
will all be punished likewise.

178
00:12:18,020 --> 00:12:18,980
- Yes. - Yes.

179
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:22,940
General!

180
00:12:22,940 --> 00:12:23,580
Move!

181
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:25,420
General! Please give me another chance.

182
00:12:26,020 --> 00:12:26,860
General!

183
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:28,460
Don’t kill me!

184
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:29,860
General!

185
00:12:41,940 --> 00:12:43,140
Since the lockdown on Liao’s side,

186
00:12:43,780 --> 00:12:46,060
we’ve enforced stricter checks

187
00:12:46,060 --> 00:12:47,540
on illegal dealings of salt and grains as well.

188
00:12:48,100 --> 00:12:49,060
Starting from today,

189
00:12:49,660 --> 00:12:51,140
violators in the army

190
00:12:51,260 --> 00:12:52,340
will be beheaded in public.

191
00:12:53,500 --> 00:12:54,980
Resentment is growing in Xixia.

192
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:56,340
According to my calculation,

193
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:57,700
when winter comes,

194
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:58,900
Xixia people

195
00:12:59,460 --> 00:13:00,780
= Illegal dealings of salt and grains =
lacking enough food to eat

196
00:13:00,780 --> 00:13:01,660
will reach over 30%.

197
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:05,180
Scouts deployed across the border

198
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:07,060
all reported that poor commoners

199
00:13:07,500 --> 00:13:08,900
and soldiers who lost their families

200
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:10,700
due to illness and famine

201
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:13,140
were waiting to revolt.

202
00:13:56,690 --> 00:13:57,370
Master,

203
00:13:57,570 --> 00:13:58,330
you’re back.

204
00:13:58,330 --> 00:13:59,020
Liaozi.

205
00:14:00,370 --> 00:14:01,260
It’s cold.

206
00:14:01,330 --> 00:14:02,610
Did you come all the way back from Yan’an?

207
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:06,300
You and Mr. Yang are both in charge of the Agency,

208
00:14:06,530 --> 00:14:08,730
yet Ren Shouzhong

209
00:14:08,730 --> 00:14:09,890
dumped all the tricky tasks

210
00:14:09,890 --> 00:14:10,700
on you.

211
00:14:12,050 --> 00:14:13,130
Are there ever tasks

212
00:14:13,210 --> 00:14:14,930
not tricky in the Agency?

213
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:16,970
How’s everything in the palace?

214
00:14:18,290 --> 00:14:19,730
Madam Zhang gave birth to a girl.

215
00:14:20,370 --> 00:14:22,050
Those waverers

216
00:14:22,210 --> 00:14:23,890
looking forward to a boy

217
00:14:23,900 --> 00:14:24,970
have become quiet.

218
00:14:25,610 --> 00:14:27,460
Xia Song was recalled to the Capital, though.

219
00:14:27,530 --> 00:14:28,290
Right after he arrived,

220
00:14:28,330 --> 00:14:29,890
his gifts were sent to Madam Zhang.

221
00:14:33,570 --> 00:14:34,500
On the seventh day of July,

222
00:14:35,170 --> 00:14:37,060
His Majesty showed no favor to her,

223
00:14:37,730 --> 00:14:38,810
but after that,

224
00:14:38,900 --> 00:14:40,450
he’s been treating her much better.

225
00:14:42,170 --> 00:14:43,130
He spends the nights with her

226
00:14:43,130 --> 00:14:44,650
most of the time

227
00:14:46,770 --> 00:14:47,610
and hasn’t visited Her Highness’s chamber

228
00:14:49,170 --> 00:14:50,930
since that day.

229
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:53,810
Many chat in private

230
00:14:54,370 --> 00:14:55,850
that had Madam Zhang

231
00:14:56,010 --> 00:14:57,010
given birth to a boy,

232
00:14:57,330 --> 00:14:58,980
Her Highness would be another Consort Jing...

233
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:03,770
Relax.

234
00:15:04,170 --> 00:15:05,770
Even if it were a boy,

235
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:08,180
she’d never make an Empress.

236
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:13,130
While flanking

237
00:15:13,650 --> 00:15:14,780
Yan’an and Guyuan,

238
00:15:15,500 --> 00:15:18,050
Yuanhao proposed peace talks in secret.

239
00:15:19,410 --> 00:15:21,050
Are reinforcements, grains and silver

240
00:15:21,170 --> 00:15:22,210
ready for Yan’an?

241
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:24,820
Yes.

242
00:15:25,700 --> 00:15:27,010
All the supplies are ready.

243
00:15:27,450 --> 00:15:28,490
Two days ago, Your Majesty

244
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,650
= Liang Huaiji =
appointed General Cao Cong to go to Yan’an.

245
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:31,810
I sent the decree

246
00:15:31,820 --> 00:15:33,410
= Chen Zhizhong, courtesy name Zhaoyu =
to summon General Cao to the Capital

247
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:34,010
for the post.

248
00:15:34,330 --> 00:15:36,050
He’s stationed 100 miles outside the Capital.

249
00:15:36,330 --> 00:15:37,970
I guess he’ll arrive today.

250
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:45,740
= Fu Bi, courtesy name Yanguo =

251
00:15:45,770 --> 00:15:47,690
Yuanhao is sneaky, dishonest

252
00:15:47,770 --> 00:15:48,730
and untrustworthy.

253
00:15:48,810 --> 00:15:49,860
His peace proposal is likely to be a scheme.

254
00:15:49,860 --> 00:15:50,770
We can’t trust him.

255
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:52,690
Sending more troops and grains

256
00:15:52,690 --> 00:15:53,570
as precautions

257
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:54,930
are sensible.

258
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:57,290
Over the three years of lockdown,

259
00:15:57,890 --> 00:15:59,140
the price of salt in our country

260
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:00,300
has inflated fivefold.

261
00:16:00,700 --> 00:16:03,010
The silk road to deliver spices and glazed tiles

262
00:16:03,010 --> 00:16:03,690
from Persia is cut off.

263
00:16:04,410 --> 00:16:05,610
The price of Rose Perfume

264
00:16:05,610 --> 00:16:07,290
arrived in Guangzhou and Ningbo

265
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:08,490
is also spiking.

266
00:16:09,610 --> 00:16:10,930
To us,

267
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,290
the lockdown reduces tea

268
00:16:12,500 --> 00:16:14,530
and silk merchants’ income

269
00:16:15,210 --> 00:16:17,010
and increases the price of salt and spices,

270
00:16:17,330 --> 00:16:19,610
but it cuts the supply of grains

271
00:16:19,610 --> 00:16:20,450
and fabrics to the enemies.

272
00:16:20,450 --> 00:16:21,330
Whose losses are bigger?

273
00:16:21,900 --> 00:16:24,210
Besides, there’s salt in our state.

274
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:26,210
Compared with mountain salt,

275
00:16:26,370 --> 00:16:27,410
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =
sea salt is expensive and bitter.

276
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:28,380
Mountain salt

277
00:16:28,380 --> 00:16:29,730
tastes better.

278
00:16:31,890 --> 00:16:32,610
I heard

279
00:16:33,210 --> 00:16:35,540
some claim that people’s lives are affected.

280
00:16:35,700 --> 00:16:36,650
They’re against the lockdown

281
00:16:36,770 --> 00:16:38,050
and suggest we negotiate for peace soon.

282
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:40,860
That’s nonsense!

283
00:16:41,170 --> 00:16:42,460
Shame on them!

284
00:16:43,050 --> 00:16:43,930
In my opinion,

285
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:45,290
those who suggested that

286
00:16:45,820 --> 00:16:47,900
are used to

287
00:16:48,210 --> 00:16:49,820
their extravagant lifestyles.

288
00:16:50,620 --> 00:16:52,010
That’s why

289
00:16:52,090 --> 00:16:53,970
a rich and powerful state like ours

290
00:16:53,970 --> 00:16:55,050
keeps losing to the less developed.

291
00:17:03,420 --> 00:17:04,140
Your Majesty.

292
00:17:04,140 --> 00:17:07,060
= Xiao Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =

293
00:17:07,090 --> 00:17:10,340
Scholar Fu omitted one thing.

294
00:17:10,850 --> 00:17:11,620
Tax.

295
00:17:13,100 --> 00:17:15,290
Tea and trade taxes

296
00:17:15,450 --> 00:17:17,060
are major sources of revenue.

297
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:21,490
Shaanxi’s been in war for years.

298
00:17:21,490 --> 00:17:22,890
Aside from the military expense,

299
00:17:23,410 --> 00:17:25,260
without taxes from tea, trade

300
00:17:25,690 --> 00:17:26,730
and spices,

301
00:17:28,010 --> 00:17:29,330
isn’t the burden

302
00:17:30,020 --> 00:17:31,530
shifted onto our people

303
00:17:31,530 --> 00:17:32,980
to make up for the losses?

304
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:37,850
This face balm smells nice.

305
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:40,810
You made it yourself?

306
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,260
Yes.

307
00:17:45,170 --> 00:17:46,290
What did you use?

308
00:17:47,330 --> 00:17:49,810
Nard, sandalwood, holy basil

309
00:17:49,810 --> 00:17:50,930
and clove, 50 grams each.

310
00:17:51,250 --> 00:17:53,210
Agastache rugosus, yellow lead, radix angelicae

311
00:17:53,210 --> 00:17:54,690
scented ink, fennel, 5 grams each.

312
00:17:54,970 --> 00:17:55,970
Ground them,

313
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:57,050
mix the powder with honey

314
00:17:57,330 --> 00:17:58,930
and put the mixture into a peony mold.

315
00:17:59,170 --> 00:18:00,330
Remove the mold once it’s dry

316
00:18:00,570 --> 00:18:01,730
and apply musk

317
00:18:01,730 --> 00:18:03,260
on the surface.

318
00:18:05,170 --> 00:18:06,010
All the ingredients

319
00:18:07,250 --> 00:18:08,850
are home-grown.

320
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:11,130
None of them is from the west.

321
00:18:11,770 --> 00:18:13,890
Trade in Shaanxi has been banned.

322
00:18:14,050 --> 00:18:15,610
The road is cut off.

323
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:17,530
Foreign ingredients are insanely expensive.

324
00:18:18,010 --> 00:18:19,330
So I changed a few recipes

325
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:21,130
with home-grown ingredients.

326
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:23,570
I tried the spices myself.

327
00:18:23,570 --> 00:18:24,450
They won’t hurt the skin.

328
00:18:27,210 --> 00:18:28,290
The crowns are elegant.

329
00:18:29,450 --> 00:18:30,610
The face balm looks nice

330
00:18:32,610 --> 00:18:33,930
and smells even better

331
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:36,930
without pricey foreign ingredients.

332
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,410
It can’t be better.

333
00:18:39,730 --> 00:18:40,530
Thank you, Your Highness.

334
00:18:42,170 --> 00:18:43,730
Qiuhe, I remember you said

335
00:18:43,900 --> 00:18:45,180
your family owns a shop

336
00:18:45,300 --> 00:18:46,410
and makes spices, too.

337
00:18:46,730 --> 00:18:47,490
Yes.

338
00:18:49,090 --> 00:18:50,300
Is this your family recipe?

339
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:53,450
My family usually makes compounded spices

340
00:18:53,810 --> 00:18:55,740
which need ingredients from the west.

341
00:18:56,410 --> 00:18:57,980
After the lockdown,

342
00:18:58,300 --> 00:18:59,530
those scented herbs and balls

343
00:18:59,530 --> 00:19:00,490
couldn’t be made.

344
00:19:00,810 --> 00:19:01,820
But I didn’t give up

345
00:19:02,050 --> 00:19:04,010
and kept finding the replacements.

346
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:05,570
After coming to the palace,

347
00:19:05,570 --> 00:19:06,930
I could get

348
00:19:07,130 --> 00:19:08,260
more flowers and powder easily,

349
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,610
so I created this.

350
00:19:11,130 --> 00:19:13,130
Have you tried to make perfume?

351
00:19:15,010 --> 00:19:16,650
The price of Rose Perfume from Persia

352
00:19:16,650 --> 00:19:17,660
is rising sharply,

353
00:19:17,820 --> 00:19:19,740
but it’s a necessity for the ladies

354
00:19:19,740 --> 00:19:21,410
to scent their clothes.

355
00:19:24,610 --> 00:19:27,370
I tried to use roses.

356
00:19:27,370 --> 00:19:28,380
Distilled rose water

357
00:19:28,530 --> 00:19:29,660
can replace the perfume

358
00:19:30,210 --> 00:19:32,420
but the scent is less strong.

359
00:19:33,850 --> 00:19:35,220
That’s acceptable.

360
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:37,780
Bring me some tomorrow.

361
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:38,890
I’ll scent my clothes with them.

362
00:19:40,100 --> 00:19:40,810
Yes.

363
00:19:43,100 --> 00:19:43,860
Qiuhe,

364
00:19:45,490 --> 00:19:47,130
what exactly are you here for?

365
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:50,210
The lockdown

366
00:19:50,570 --> 00:19:51,860
hurts Xixia much more

367
00:19:51,860 --> 00:19:53,210
than it does us.

368
00:19:53,930 --> 00:19:56,170
Whether the petition for peace is sincere or not,

369
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:58,130
it excludes abandoning the imperial title

370
00:19:58,490 --> 00:20:00,690
and surrendering themselves to Your Majesty

371
00:20:01,420 --> 00:20:02,570
but asks for money,

372
00:20:02,570 --> 00:20:04,530
fabrics and tea granted by the Founding Father

373
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:06,090
after their first surrender.

374
00:20:06,490 --> 00:20:07,940
And they want to reopen the markets.

375
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:10,570
I support Fu Bi.

376
00:20:10,820 --> 00:20:11,850
This kind of petition

377
00:20:12,090 --> 00:20:13,250
must be sternly denied.

378
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:19,290
Zhizhong,

379
00:20:20,570 --> 00:20:21,730
head to the Cao Mansion.

380
00:20:22,620 --> 00:20:23,650
When Cao Cong arrives,

381
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:25,170
help him to make preparations

382
00:20:25,170 --> 00:20:26,250
for the upcoming trip.

383
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:27,930
Give him

384
00:20:28,420 --> 00:20:29,450
whatever he needs.

385
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:32,970
Tell him

386
00:20:33,570 --> 00:20:34,970
to pay the Empress a visit before he leaves.

387
00:20:36,810 --> 00:20:37,970
Yes, Your Majesty.

388
00:20:45,820 --> 00:20:47,340
Prime Minister Lv has been sick for over half a month.

389
00:20:48,370 --> 00:20:49,650
He was getting better

390
00:20:50,050 --> 00:20:52,330
but the snow lately

391
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:53,810
worsens his condition.

392
00:20:54,570 --> 00:20:55,490
Xia Song, Dexiang,

393
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,330
please check on him for me.

394
00:21:00,530 --> 00:21:01,690
Yes, Your Majesty.

395
00:21:15,570 --> 00:21:17,370
Is the comparison of officials in history

396
00:21:17,970 --> 00:21:18,850
completed?

397
00:21:23,530 --> 00:21:26,090
The number of our officials

398
00:21:26,290 --> 00:21:27,730
does top the list.

399
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:31,930
According to historical records,

400
00:21:32,730 --> 00:21:34,620
over the 200-year-reign of the Eastern Han Dynasty,

401
00:21:34,650 --> 00:21:37,930
there were 7,567 officials in total.

402
00:21:38,570 --> 00:21:42,260
The number in Jin was 6,836.

403
00:21:42,650 --> 00:21:43,810
In Sui,

404
00:21:43,810 --> 00:21:46,090
it reached 12,576.

405
00:21:46,570 --> 00:21:48,250
It amounted to 18,050

406
00:21:48,490 --> 00:21:51,700
in the 300-year-old Tang Dynasty.

407
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:54,530
Our reign has lasted less than 80 years,

408
00:21:54,900 --> 00:21:55,930
but it’s already over 10,000.

409
00:21:56,900 --> 00:21:58,810
If we calculate

410
00:21:58,810 --> 00:22:00,780
the number of officials per 100,000 people have,

411
00:22:01,010 --> 00:22:02,820
it’ll be 13 in Eastern Han,

412
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:05,210
42 in Jin,

413
00:22:05,570 --> 00:22:07,300
27 in Sui,

414
00:22:07,620 --> 00:22:09,540
35 in Tang.

415
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,610
In the reign of our late Emperor,

416
00:22:11,900 --> 00:22:13,580
the number reached 45,

417
00:22:14,130 --> 00:22:16,330
and now, it’ll be even larger.

418
00:22:17,770 --> 00:22:19,290
You went to Yan’an alone

419
00:22:19,290 --> 00:22:20,300
to ask the general

420
00:22:20,970 --> 00:22:23,690
to replace your grandfather
to be an army physician?

421
00:22:24,370 --> 00:22:25,170
Yes.

422
00:22:25,900 --> 00:22:27,780
My grandfather is over 60 years old

423
00:22:27,780 --> 00:22:28,940
who has a chronic cough.

424
00:22:29,570 --> 00:22:30,610
Life in the army is hard.

425
00:22:30,900 --> 00:22:32,730
It’s too much for people his age.

426
00:22:33,810 --> 00:22:36,250
In terms of cleaning and treating wounds,

427
00:22:36,250 --> 00:22:38,220
fixing broken bones and stopping the bleeding,

428
00:22:38,580 --> 00:22:40,140
I’m as good as my grandfather.

429
00:22:41,010 --> 00:22:42,250
You’re a girl.

430
00:22:42,930 --> 00:22:44,620
Having you in the army is inconvenient.

431
00:22:45,300 --> 00:22:46,980
It’s right to deny your request.

432
00:22:48,850 --> 00:22:49,740
I know,

433
00:22:50,690 --> 00:22:51,610
but

434
00:22:52,530 --> 00:22:54,490
I had to try for my grandfather.

435
00:22:59,500 --> 00:23:01,380
No wonder Maoze appreciates you.

436
00:23:06,210 --> 00:23:07,890
He’s insightful.

437
00:23:13,930 --> 00:23:14,860
When the Founding Father was in charge,

438
00:23:15,490 --> 00:23:17,100
almost half of the revenue was left each year.

439
00:23:17,410 --> 00:23:18,330
During the reign of the late Emperor,

440
00:23:18,490 --> 00:23:19,610
there was a deficit every year.

441
00:23:20,210 --> 00:23:21,090
Your Majesty,

442
00:23:21,090 --> 00:23:21,970
you promote business,

443
00:23:22,370 --> 00:23:24,130
so the business tax revenue keeps surging.

444
00:23:24,450 --> 00:23:25,450
Take last year as an example.

445
00:23:25,650 --> 00:23:26,690
Our revenue was

446
00:23:26,730 --> 00:23:28,500
fourfold larger than that of the Founding Father,

447
00:23:29,170 --> 00:23:31,780
yet we could barely make ends meet.

448
00:23:36,700 --> 00:23:37,660
I don’t think

449
00:23:37,780 --> 00:23:39,140
I waged sanguinary wars

450
00:23:39,450 --> 00:23:40,570
or built new buildings for pleasure.

451
00:23:40,780 --> 00:23:41,081
Your Majesty, you are thrifty.

452
00:23:42,210 --> 00:23:43,330
The problem lies in the excess of officials.

453
00:23:44,410 --> 00:23:45,130
First,

454
00:23:45,650 --> 00:23:47,250
many positions overlap with each other.

455
00:23:47,250 --> 00:23:48,490
More money is spent yet the efficiency decreases.

456
00:23:48,490 --> 00:23:49,580
Only arguments grow.

457
00:23:49,890 --> 00:23:50,530
Second,

458
00:23:50,730 --> 00:23:52,130
only a few positions are powerful.

459
00:23:52,250 --> 00:23:53,130
Those eager

460
00:23:53,130 --> 00:23:54,090
to gain power

461
00:23:54,090 --> 00:23:55,090
bribe officials in charge.

462
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:57,210
Feng Shiyuan was corrupted like that.

463
00:23:57,450 --> 00:23:58,100
Hence,

464
00:23:58,370 --> 00:24:00,020
a net of bribery and corruption is established.

465
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:01,890
Money is squandered.

466
00:24:02,490 --> 00:24:03,610
Laws are disregarded.

467
00:24:03,850 --> 00:24:05,090
Principles are ignored.

468
00:24:05,490 --> 00:24:06,290
Well said!

469
00:24:07,780 --> 00:24:08,490
So,

470
00:24:09,010 --> 00:24:10,330
this problem must be dealt with.

471
00:24:10,850 --> 00:24:12,690
The officer-selecting system must be changed.

472
00:24:14,380 --> 00:24:15,210
Change the system?

473
00:24:16,650 --> 00:24:17,690
Why weren’t there

474
00:24:17,690 --> 00:24:19,290
so many officials at first?

475
00:24:20,450 --> 00:24:21,610
Because we started from scratch.

476
00:24:21,850 --> 00:24:22,740
We had nothing back then.

477
00:24:23,730 --> 00:24:24,810
Yet after three generations,

478
00:24:25,330 --> 00:24:26,260
a problem once small

479
00:24:26,580 --> 00:24:28,330
has grown tenfold.

480
00:24:29,450 --> 00:24:30,650
That’s precise.

481
00:24:30,970 --> 00:24:32,860
But changing the officer-selecting system

482
00:24:32,860 --> 00:24:33,820
concerns the foundation of our state.

483
00:24:34,180 --> 00:24:36,210
The leader of it should be selected first.

484
00:24:36,450 --> 00:24:37,490
Officials in the Cabinet and Privy Council...

485
00:24:46,050 --> 00:24:47,090
Officials in the Cabinet and Privy Council

486
00:24:47,250 --> 00:24:49,330
lack innovation, courage

487
00:24:49,330 --> 00:24:50,410
and determination.

488
00:24:54,130 --> 00:24:55,930
I agree with Fu Bi.

489
00:24:56,610 --> 00:24:58,410
Zhang Dexiang is too conservative.

490
00:24:58,530 --> 00:25:00,290
Chen Zhizhong’s talent is limited.

491
00:25:00,570 --> 00:25:02,570
Xia Song’s reputation is controversial.

492
00:25:03,050 --> 00:25:03,930
As for me,

493
00:25:04,580 --> 00:25:07,130
I wasn’t adventurous when I was young,

494
00:25:07,450 --> 00:25:10,060
and now, I’m more tentative

495
00:25:10,450 --> 00:25:12,050
and indecisive.

496
00:25:16,890 --> 00:25:18,570
Who says the leader of the reform

497
00:25:18,770 --> 00:25:20,890
must be from the Cabinet and Privy Council?

498
00:25:35,460 --> 00:25:38,220
= Ouyang Xiu, courtesy name Yongshu =

499
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:39,980
Youheng told me in the letter

500
00:25:40,300 --> 00:25:42,660
that she went to the palace
on the first day of spring.

501
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:44,980
= Ouyang Xiu’s wife, Xue Youxi =
When she and the Empress read spring festival scrolls,

502
00:25:45,380 --> 00:25:47,220
His Majesty happened to pass by her chamber.

503
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:48,180
Knowing that Youheng was inside,

504
00:25:48,460 --> 00:25:49,380
he smiled and said

505
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:51,100
when the Dragon Boat Festival arrived,

506
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:51,780
Su Zimei

507
00:25:51,780 --> 00:25:53,340
would no longer be in the limelight alone.

508
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,500
After Youheng said that to Zimei,

509
00:25:55,500 --> 00:25:56,500
Zimei became excited and said,

510
00:25:56,940 --> 00:25:58,620
“Will Ouyang Yongshu

511
00:25:58,620 --> 00:26:00,020
or Fan Xiwen soon be back to the Capital?”

512
00:26:01,420 --> 00:26:02,380
Shortly after that,

513
00:26:02,780 --> 00:26:04,700
His Majesty did recall you to the Capital

514
00:26:04,780 --> 00:26:06,300
and reinstate you.

515
00:26:08,940 --> 00:26:10,140
You suffered a lot with me.

516
00:26:14,580 --> 00:26:15,460
But

517
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:18,380
if Zhigui and Xiwen

518
00:26:19,780 --> 00:26:21,660
could be back soon,

519
00:26:22,940 --> 00:26:24,220
that’d be bliss.

520
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:38,180
= Liang Yuansheng =

521
00:26:38,180 --> 00:26:38,900
Sir.

522
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:42,340
= Han Qi, courtesy name Zhigui =
I’ve completed the transfer order.

523
00:26:42,940 --> 00:26:43,780
You can

524
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:45,740
fill in the paperwork at your superior’s office

525
00:26:46,100 --> 00:26:47,100
and pack up

526
00:26:47,580 --> 00:26:49,140
to work for General Di Qing.

527
00:26:50,620 --> 00:26:53,300
General Di is mighty, brave,

528
00:26:53,500 --> 00:26:54,500
smart and persistent.

529
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:57,380
He learns to read and write from Fan Xiwen.

530
00:26:57,740 --> 00:26:58,980
His future is promising.

531
00:26:59,620 --> 00:27:01,180
Hone your skills with him.

532
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:04,420
I have high hopes on you.

533
00:27:08,620 --> 00:27:10,500
I won’t disappoint you

534
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,180
and I’ll do my best.

535
00:27:17,900 --> 00:27:19,020
Are you leaving so soon

536
00:27:19,460 --> 00:27:20,740
without a guard?

537
00:27:21,300 --> 00:27:21,980
I escorted

538
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:23,260
Mr. Liu to the Capital.

539
00:27:23,340 --> 00:27:24,620
Let me...

540
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:25,780
No need.

541
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:31,780
Are you really going

542
00:27:31,780 --> 00:27:32,900
to take all the blames?

543
00:27:35,220 --> 00:27:37,180
Those at the frontier said

544
00:27:37,620 --> 00:27:39,740
General Ren Fu changed the strategy

545
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:41,580
and didn’t follow your order.

546
00:27:42,220 --> 00:27:43,100
I’m Commander-in-Chief.

547
00:27:43,860 --> 00:27:45,220
Selecting the right general

548
00:27:45,460 --> 00:27:46,380
for the battle

549
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:48,300
falls under my responsibility.

550
00:27:49,140 --> 00:27:50,660
How could I shirk it due to the loss?

551
00:27:51,340 --> 00:27:52,220
Besides,

552
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:56,420
I underestimated the enemy and was overambitious.

553
00:27:56,780 --> 00:27:58,140
I wasn’t cautious enough.

554
00:27:58,540 --> 00:28:00,780
The inferiors follow the superiors’ examples.

555
00:28:02,180 --> 00:28:02,900
What’s more,

556
00:28:03,820 --> 00:28:06,100
General Ren and his son both died.

557
00:28:07,140 --> 00:28:08,140
Even if he was at fault,

558
00:28:08,740 --> 00:28:10,140
he had already paid with his life.

559
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:13,460
How could I damage his posthumous reputation?

560
00:28:15,540 --> 00:28:18,140
Don’t mention this to anyone again.

561
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:21,940
Let’s go.

562
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:45,660
Lesson learned.

563
00:28:52,610 --> 00:28:54,250
Would you like some tea, sir?

564
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:56,220
- Due to the war in recent years, - Have a look.

565
00:28:56,340 --> 00:28:57,580
checks are more rigorous

566
00:28:57,740 --> 00:28:58,980
to keep spies of Xixia at bay.

567
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:02,140
Song offered us money

568
00:29:02,140 --> 00:29:03,220
to form an alliance.

569
00:29:03,820 --> 00:29:05,260
Markets at the border are closed.

570
00:29:06,140 --> 00:29:07,140
They’ve lost their minds.

571
00:29:07,140 --> 00:29:07,900
Over the past year,

572
00:29:08,060 --> 00:29:09,820
they’ve been stirring up trouble at the border.

573
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:12,860
Xiwen.

574
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:15,140
Xiwen.

575
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:15,860
Prime Minister Yan.

576
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,500
You look travel-stained.

577
00:29:22,980 --> 00:29:24,060
It’s been a while.

578
00:29:30,860 --> 00:29:32,060
= Fan Zhongyan, courtesy name Xiwen =
Within a month,

579
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:35,060
I was ordered to come back in three urgent letters

580
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:37,620
before the new year court meeting.

581
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:39,260
Right after I entered the Capital,

582
00:29:39,340 --> 00:29:41,060
you came to welcome me yourself,
Prime Minister Yan.

583
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:44,340
I’m a bit nervous.

584
00:29:44,620 --> 00:29:45,500
Don’t be.

585
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:47,220
I’m not sent by His Majesty

586
00:29:47,220 --> 00:29:49,100
to arrest you and bring you to him.

587
00:29:50,900 --> 00:29:52,620
I came for old times’ sake.

588
00:29:56,220 --> 00:29:58,180
We indeed have known each other for long.

589
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:00,100
No,

590
00:30:00,940 --> 00:30:02,940
I didn’t mean us.

591
00:30:07,260 --> 00:30:08,340
Since the winter came,

592
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:10,180
Prime Minister Lv’s cough has deteriorated.

593
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:13,060
He’s been in bed for two months.

594
00:30:13,260 --> 00:30:14,100
I’m afraid

595
00:30:14,580 --> 00:30:15,900
his days are numbered.

596
00:30:17,260 --> 00:30:18,500
When I visited him,

597
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:20,540
he mentioned you a few times,

598
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:22,620
saying conflicts between you two

599
00:30:23,020 --> 00:30:25,340
implicated almost half of the court.

600
00:30:26,220 --> 00:30:27,340
He was emotional about that.

601
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:29,500
I’m thinking

602
00:30:31,060 --> 00:30:32,180
throughout our life,

603
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,660
we’re lucky

604
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:35,900
to work with each other

605
00:30:36,620 --> 00:30:37,700
even if we have disagreements.

606
00:30:42,140 --> 00:30:43,700
I should visit Prime Minster Lv.

607
00:30:45,820 --> 00:30:47,980
Our disagreements are only work-related.

608
00:30:48,540 --> 00:30:49,900
I was arrogant

609
00:30:50,140 --> 00:30:51,060
and sharp-tongued in the past.

610
00:30:52,020 --> 00:30:53,980
I’m younger than him after all

611
00:30:54,460 --> 00:30:56,100
and might not have shown him enough respect.

612
00:31:04,820 --> 00:31:05,500
Prime Minister Lv.

613
00:31:06,140 --> 00:31:08,780
= Lv Yijian, courtesy name Tanfu =
Prime Minister Yan and Scholar Fan came to visit.

614
00:31:14,620 --> 00:31:15,980
Fan who?

615
00:31:21,900 --> 00:31:24,660
Prime Minister Lv, Zhongyan came to visit you.

616
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,060
Fan Xiwen?

617
00:31:26,940 --> 00:31:29,300
Sit. Sit down.

618
00:31:33,860 --> 00:31:34,540
Sit.

619
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,340
Have a seat.

620
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:46,140
I have a few things to tell you.

621
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:51,300
Redundant officials

622
00:31:53,740 --> 00:31:55,020
are too big a burden

623
00:31:56,020 --> 00:31:59,300
to our state.

624
00:32:01,940 --> 00:32:06,100
I’m always against the reform,

625
00:32:06,460 --> 00:32:09,100
but I know His Majesty well.

626
00:32:10,460 --> 00:32:12,380
If I understand him correctly,

627
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:16,780
His Majesty intends to appoint you

628
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:20,180
to reduce officials and soldiers.

629
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:24,020
Keep this in mind.

630
00:32:25,020 --> 00:32:28,380
The traditional system may not be perfect,

631
00:32:30,020 --> 00:32:31,860
but if you make wrong changes,

632
00:32:32,740 --> 00:32:34,420
resulting in a worse system,

633
00:32:35,620 --> 00:32:38,100
both you and His Majesty

634
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:42,780
will be sinners of our country.

635
00:32:46,420 --> 00:32:48,740
Believe it or not,

636
00:32:49,740 --> 00:32:52,260
His Majesty’s target is redundancy.

637
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:55,660
He wants it to shrink

638
00:32:57,460 --> 00:32:59,540
but dares not

639
00:33:01,340 --> 00:33:03,820
to right the ancestors’ wrongs.

640
00:33:17,860 --> 00:33:21,580
= Cui Bai, courtesy name Zixi =

641
00:33:29,380 --> 00:33:30,140
Your Majesty.

642
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:33,660
Preparations for tomorrow’s morning court

643
00:33:34,300 --> 00:33:36,620
have been completed as planned.

644
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:38,980
Is there anything else you’d like to add?

645
00:33:40,100 --> 00:33:40,780
Nothing.

646
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:41,740
You may leave.

647
00:33:43,420 --> 00:33:44,100
Yes.

648
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,020
Your Majesty.

649
00:33:52,140 --> 00:33:53,260
Go to bed early.

650
00:33:53,460 --> 00:33:54,860
You have a long day tomorrow.

651
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:02,540
Let’s go take a walk.

652
00:34:02,800 --> 00:34:03,060
Yes.

653
00:34:19,020 --> 00:34:21,260
= Gate of Peace =

654
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:22,020
Your Majesty.

655
00:34:41,780 --> 00:34:44,220
= Princess Huirou =

656
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:45,540
It is Qiuhe

657
00:34:45,620 --> 00:34:47,460
in this painting,

658
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,100
but

659
00:34:49,580 --> 00:34:51,660
she looks different

660
00:34:51,660 --> 00:34:52,740
from the person I see.

661
00:34:54,740 --> 00:34:55,900
Being able to sense the difference

662
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,300
shows that

663
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:58,340
you’ve already improved.

664
00:35:00,620 --> 00:35:03,780
But this is no other but Qiuhe.

665
00:35:04,860 --> 00:35:06,380
The eyes, nose, eyebrows

666
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:07,340
are identical.

667
00:35:08,620 --> 00:35:11,060
Mr. Cui painted it himself. How could it be wrong?

668
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:13,940
It’s not wrong,

669
00:35:14,860 --> 00:35:16,100
but in the portrait

670
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,420
is Stewardess of Perfume-Making Qiuhe,

671
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:21,700
not the one serving me, His Majesty,

672
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,500
you and concubines.

673
00:35:28,020 --> 00:35:28,820
These paintings

674
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:29,860
have been well-known by others.

675
00:35:30,580 --> 00:35:31,620
On the last day of painting,

676
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:34,460
all Imperial Artists were busy copying it.

677
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:36,420
When I had tea

678
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:37,460
with ladies of the royal family yesterday,

679
00:35:37,660 --> 00:35:39,140
many of them asked about it.

680
00:35:39,380 --> 00:35:40,260
That’s right.

681
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:41,540
These four paintings are a set.

682
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:43,620
Each is named with a perfume

683
00:35:43,620 --> 00:35:45,340
made by the stewardess in the portrait.

684
00:35:46,220 --> 00:35:48,020
Right after Mr. Cui’s painting was framed,

685
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,620
there were fake copies

686
00:35:49,620 --> 00:35:51,140
outside the palace already.

687
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,660
In the first month of the year,

688
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:57,620
banquets and celebrations go one after another.

689
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,740
There’s nothing new.

690
00:36:01,340 --> 00:36:02,620
These paintings

691
00:36:02,860 --> 00:36:04,100
give me an idea.

692
00:36:05,100 --> 00:36:06,660
Why don’t we hold a perfume competition?

693
00:36:07,180 --> 00:36:07,980
The rule is simple.

694
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,460
All the ingredients

695
00:36:10,020 --> 00:36:12,020
must be home-grown.

696
00:36:12,220 --> 00:36:13,300
His Majesty has arrived.

697
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:21,580
Please don’t tell father that I’m here.

698
00:36:21,620 --> 00:36:22,580
I want to surprise him.

699
00:36:24,740 --> 00:36:25,540
His Majesty is here.

700
00:36:26,060 --> 00:36:27,380
= Ms. Xiu =
He finally comes!

701
00:36:28,260 --> 00:36:29,260
I’ll go get liquor.

702
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:31,620
And desserts.

703
00:36:39,500 --> 00:36:40,700
The chamber is brightly lit.

704
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,540
What are you doing?

705
00:36:42,780 --> 00:36:43,460
Your Majesty.

706
00:36:45,540 --> 00:36:47,020
Paintings arrived from the Imperial Art Academy.

707
00:36:55,660 --> 00:36:56,660
Cui Bai’s paintings?

708
00:37:00,380 --> 00:37:01,220
Is this...

709
00:37:02,260 --> 00:37:03,540
the combing maid

710
00:37:03,540 --> 00:37:04,420
Zhang Maoze brought into the palace?

711
00:37:07,140 --> 00:37:09,860
Not only Xinhe likes her

712
00:37:10,020 --> 00:37:11,140
but you like her even more.

713
00:37:12,140 --> 00:37:13,020
In this case,

714
00:37:13,660 --> 00:37:14,460
you could’ve promoted her

715
00:37:14,460 --> 00:37:16,060
to Chief of Styling.

716
00:37:16,060 --> 00:37:17,020
It was nothing wrong

717
00:37:17,660 --> 00:37:19,140
and within your power.

718
00:37:21,260 --> 00:37:22,340
At first, I thought

719
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:24,020
Dong Qiuhe was young

720
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:26,300
and inexperienced. She had a lot to learn,

721
00:37:26,740 --> 00:37:28,060
so I didn’t promote her.

722
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,300
After observing her lately,

723
00:37:31,020 --> 00:37:32,980
I think she’s more capable

724
00:37:33,060 --> 00:37:34,700
than some experienced maids.

725
00:37:35,660 --> 00:37:37,020
I’ve asked Ren Shouzhong

726
00:37:37,020 --> 00:37:37,820
to prepare the paperwork

727
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,100
for her promotion.

728
00:38:01,660 --> 00:38:02,620
Although

729
00:38:02,740 --> 00:38:04,140
I haven’t been here for six months,

730
00:38:05,100 --> 00:38:07,860
nothing has changed.

731
00:38:20,060 --> 00:38:21,260
You didn’t come

732
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:26,380
or give me any punishment.

733
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:27,740
I was too slow

734
00:38:28,540 --> 00:38:29,500
to realize

735
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:30,660
my own mistakes,

736
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:33,620
so I took it as you are too busy

737
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:35,260
to visit me.

738
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:37,020
And my life continues as usual.

739
00:38:41,460 --> 00:38:43,100
You did nothing wrong.

740
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:44,900
How could you be wrong?

741
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:47,180
Even when Concubine Zhang

742
00:38:47,180 --> 00:38:48,220
asked to borrow your sedan,

743
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:49,420
you lent it to her without hesitation.

744
00:38:49,740 --> 00:38:51,300
I had to educate her myself

745
00:38:51,300 --> 00:38:53,260
that she should act according to her rank.

746
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:07,340
Madam Zhang asked for a new sedan

747
00:39:07,940 --> 00:39:09,580
or the one I was using.

748
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:11,420
I checked hers.

749
00:39:11,420 --> 00:39:13,340
It was old but still usable,

750
00:39:13,740 --> 00:39:14,420
and it wasn’t older

751
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:15,980
than other concubines’ sedans.

752
00:39:17,340 --> 00:39:18,980
You always advocate thrift,

753
00:39:19,420 --> 00:39:20,980
so I dared not

754
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:23,140
give new sedans to all the concubines.

755
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:26,780
But back then, Madam Zhang’s due date was coming.

756
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:30,060
I was afraid she’d be unsafe in the old sedan,

757
00:39:31,420 --> 00:39:32,540
so I agreed

758
00:39:32,540 --> 00:39:34,340
to let her use mine for once

759
00:39:34,340 --> 00:39:35,300
after serious consideration.

760
00:39:38,140 --> 00:39:39,260
I thought

761
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:40,980
it was

762
00:39:41,220 --> 00:39:42,900
the best option out of the worst,

763
00:39:44,420 --> 00:39:46,060
yet I didn’t expect

764
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,220
it was still the worst in your eyes.

765
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:53,860
So

766
00:39:53,900 --> 00:39:55,900
even after so much consideration,

767
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:57,780
you still

768
00:39:57,780 --> 00:39:58,980
put the rules behind.

769
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:07,020
I intend to have everyone

770
00:40:07,020 --> 00:40:08,340
follow the rules.

771
00:40:09,620 --> 00:40:10,700
But ever since Madam Zhang

772
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:12,060
was a dancer,

773
00:40:12,420 --> 00:40:14,100
after I punished her for her mistakes,

774
00:40:14,500 --> 00:40:16,020
you went to comfort her.

775
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:18,540
However many rules there are,

776
00:40:18,780 --> 00:40:20,900
officials must obey Emperor
and wives must obey their husbands.

777
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:24,420
If I offended you

778
00:40:25,020 --> 00:40:26,140
and infuriated you

779
00:40:26,140 --> 00:40:26,980
because of Madam Zhang,

780
00:40:26,980 --> 00:40:28,380
I’d be a sinner.

781
00:40:32,580 --> 00:40:33,420
But...

782
00:40:35,060 --> 00:40:36,620
I was wrong this time.

783
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,620
If I gave Madam Zhang a new sedan,

784
00:40:41,180 --> 00:40:42,620
others with the same rank would find it unfair,

785
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:43,460
so I didn’t.

786
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:45,780
But what did you do?

787
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:48,020
You gave it to her

788
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:51,740
and nobody in the harem complained about it.

789
00:40:55,100 --> 00:40:57,620
I’m sure everyone here

790
00:40:58,820 --> 00:40:59,900
has finally realized

791
00:40:59,900 --> 00:41:00,860
if not before

792
00:41:03,860 --> 00:41:05,180
that Madam Zhang is different

793
00:41:05,180 --> 00:41:06,020
from other women.

794
00:41:11,180 --> 00:41:12,100
Your Highness.

795
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:15,860
There’s one last jar

796
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:17,140
of His Majesty’s favorite liquor Moyao.

797
00:41:26,100 --> 00:41:26,900
Moyao?

798
00:41:28,620 --> 00:41:30,100
I haven’t drunk that for a while.

799
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:45,020
I was too occupied with work

800
00:41:45,940 --> 00:41:46,940
to find time to visit you.

801
00:41:48,300 --> 00:41:49,820
Tomorrow is the grand court meeting.

802
00:41:50,380 --> 00:41:52,620
There will be various events after that,

803
00:41:53,940 --> 00:41:56,340
whipping cows, viewing lanterns,
visiting Shangqing Temple

804
00:41:57,420 --> 00:41:59,420
scheduled for the concubines to attend.

805
00:42:00,100 --> 00:42:01,140
Rest assured.

806
00:42:02,420 --> 00:42:04,300
I’ve made the arrangements.

807
00:42:10,620 --> 00:42:12,780
The details are recorded in the book.

808
00:42:13,380 --> 00:42:14,340
If you want to have a look,

809
00:42:14,340 --> 00:42:15,660
I’ll ask Ling’er to bring it to you.

810
00:42:17,220 --> 00:42:18,620
It’s lengthy, though.

811
00:42:19,300 --> 00:42:20,300
Compared with last year,

812
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:21,300
not many changes are made,

813
00:42:21,660 --> 00:42:22,900
so I didn’t bother you

814
00:42:22,900 --> 00:42:23,860
with them.

815
00:42:24,700 --> 00:42:25,660
I can never

816
00:42:26,180 --> 00:42:27,860
find flaws in your work.

817
00:42:29,700 --> 00:42:30,540
Even without me,

818
00:42:31,340 --> 00:42:33,860
the entire harem still respects you

819
00:42:34,460 --> 00:42:35,860
and all officials speak highly of you.

820
00:42:51,490 --> 00:43:01,150
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

821
00:43:02,490 --> 00:43:10,830
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

822
00:43:13,670 --> 00:43:18,390
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

823
00:43:19,370 --> 00:43:23,530
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

824
00:43:24,970 --> 00:43:30,450
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

825
00:43:30,450 --> 00:43:35,240
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

826
00:43:38,900 --> 00:43:44,540
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

827
00:43:44,540 --> 00:43:49,450
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

828
00:43:49,950 --> 00:43:55,710
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

829
00:43:55,710 --> 00:44:00,800
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

830
00:44:01,230 --> 00:44:06,160
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

831
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:11,630
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

832
00:44:12,320 --> 00:44:17,470
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

833
00:44:17,970 --> 00:44:23,010
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

834
00:44:23,550 --> 00:44:27,620
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

835
00:44:29,090 --> 00:44:33,730
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

836
00:44:34,750 --> 00:44:39,910
♪ The howling wind ♪

837
00:44:40,280 --> 00:44:44,350
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

838
00:44:45,830 --> 00:44:50,750
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

839
00:44:51,410 --> 00:44:56,630
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

840
00:44:57,050 --> 00:45:02,330
♪ The howling wind ♪

841
00:45:02,620 --> 00:45:07,520
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

842
00:45:08,110 --> 00:45:14,820
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
